Who wants to win a fully-decorated, interactive, customized playhouse? #ad @KinderUS is partnering with us to give two families the chance to win a Charmed Playhouse. #KinderJoy's latest treat will include five Barbie characters that help kids imagine all they can be such as a scientist, DJ, baker, athlete and movie director. We are building two playhouses, a French patisserie for the baker and a dance club for the DJ. Two families will win one of these playhouses, built to inspire the message, "You can be anything!" Please visit kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com or click on the link in our bio to enter the Kinder Joy x Barbie, "You Can Be Anything Sweepstakes." 

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. Open only to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and DC who are 18 years of age or older with a valid email account as of the date of entry. node.text:
I can't think of many things that are more exciting for us than giving a playhouse away to a deserving family. #ad I have been waiting in anticipation to announce that we are teaming up with @KinderUS to do just that! #KinderJoy is releasing a new treat that features inspirational Barbie characters to help kids imagine all that they can be. We are building playhouses based on two of these characters, a French patisserie (bakery) for the baker and a dance club for the DJ. We will be going all out on each one! We are so excited to join these brands and help inspire the two winning families to dream big and pursue their passions through play. To enter, parents can visit kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com or click on the link in our bio. 

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. Open only to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and DC who are 18 years of age or older with a valid email account as of the date of entry. Sweepstakes begin at 12:00 a.m. ET on 8/25/21 and ends at 11:59 p.m. ET on 9/17/21. Void in Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico and where prohibited. For complete details, see Official Rules available at www.kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com Sponsor: Ferrero U.S.A., Inc., Parsippany, NJ 07054
